name: SUCalendar
0:
”Alexa, open Cuse calendar”
”Ask Cuse calendar to get me events for today”
”What events are happening on August 1st”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: cuse calendar
des: Are you a kind of a student who always misses attending any interesting event you wanted to attend but being lazy to keep track of the event calendar or do you just want to know what's happening at Syracuse University? Just ask Alexa with cuse calendar about the events and get event details that you don't want to miss.
